454
00:19:59,357 --> 00:20:00,302
<i>Bye.</i>

455
00:20:08,046 --> 00:20:09,860
- Hey, Oscar ?
- Quoi de neuf Pam ?

456
00:20:10,156 --> 00:20:13,352
